extends layout.pug



block content 

  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro

    div

      h1 My Portfolio

      p.lead.text-light

        | In my portfolio you will find some of the projects I have completed during my JavaScript FullStack Techdegree at TeamTreehouse. | I have gained a myriad of skills to add to my professional experience with back end development.Having gained these new skills concerning front end development, | will make me a valuable asset at my current employment and any future endeavors.Having worked on the business side of processes, then back - end development and now | the skills as a developer allows me to wear many hats including that of a Business Analyst as I understand the needs | of end user and I can develop internal and external applications to meet the business requirements more concisely.

  article.grid-container.portfolio-index

    

    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

    
        each project in projects
          .cell
             a(href='/project/' + project.id)
              img.thumbnail(src= project.image_urls[0])
              h5 #{project_name}


